{"type": "article", "id": 8726, "title": "“Catch My Drip ” 雨伞托", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-21T06:59:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234942rwh0p21CDIBiqkcK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自魁北克的设计工作室 Non-Useless 推出了这款名为 “Catch My Drip ” 的雨伞托，试图为我们解决雨伞拿进屋子里面来之后湿答答弄脏家具的问题。伞托规格为 3.5 X 6.5 寸，有着圆滑的外形，采用蒙特利尔当地材料，全手工制作而成，看上去小巧精致，像是把普通的雨伞都变成了一件装饰品。摆在架子上，甚至可以用滴灌的方法给植物浇水。售价为 404 元人民币，<a href=\"http://nonuseless.com/product/umbrella-holder-doorstop-the-non-useless-team-choose-the-color-for-you-53874/1-color-114825\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。里面也可以看到他们更多的作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234939fYtPj3Cez8EgTs7K.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58557457\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234940pOgv6wxNFc5GrkQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052349407Gn5oDrwzTuV2BX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.56723716\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234941X2roNGOuCpVzS7qn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.40953545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234941kGfEuPd3icSHjamr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.50366748\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}